This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as dependency parsing. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new neural network architecture for parsing. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of machine learning techniques for language understanding. The use of GPUs and parallel processing also suggests a possible categorization under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of convolutional neural networks and graph-based approaches could also make it relevant to cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-category.
